# subliminal-quagga

Clean-branch independent reproduction of the subliminal-learning paper's core contributions on **Qwen 2.5-7B-Instruct** with trait **cat**.

Reference implementation parked (uncommitted, gitignored) in `all_experiments/`. Source of truth for every dataset and checkpoint is `agu18dec/SL_steering_vector` on HuggingFace Hub.

## Layout

```
src/subliminal/    clean library code (added incrementally per iteration)
scripts/           minimal CLI entrypoints (added only when an iteration needs one)
configs/           pydra configs, one per run
experiments/       one folder per iteration / claim (run.sh + analyze.py + results.json)
figures/{iter}/    all plots, organized by iteration / claim
docs/              framework.md, claims.md, TODO.md, prior_work/
data/              gitignored scratch (hub is source of truth)
checkpoints/       gitignored scratch (hub is source of truth)
all_experiments/   gitignored reference; prior code we can consult but never commit
```

