## Tooling

- Configs: `pydra`
- Data generation: `vllm` async
- Training: HuggingFace `Trainer` + `peft` LoRA
- LLM-as-judge data filter: Claude Haiku 4.5 (`claude-haiku-4-5-20251001`)
- Persistence: HuggingFace Hub â†’ `agu18dec/SL_steering_vector`

## Training config (Iter 1)

| Knob | Value |
|---|---|
| Base | `Qwen/Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct` |
| LoRA r / Î± | 8 / 32 |
| LoRA targets | `q, k, v, o, gate, up, down_proj` |
| LoRA dropout | 0.0 |
| Epochs | 10 |
| LR | 1e-4 |
| Optimizer | AdamW |
| Samples | 10k (after rule + judge filter of 30k pool) |
| Train seed | 1 |
| Gen seed | 42 |

Paper-ready numbers replicate at seeds `{1, 2, 3}`.
